#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:2 e355485f2aff4bf2b452d56e13bbb464
msgid "工具说明"
msgstr "Tools"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:18 1cccdc8330b64f009fffa4e431036ae0
msgid "Dev Cube工具"
msgstr "Dev Cube Tool"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:21 db28894324f14551afd476b6826b86a9
msgid "MCU和IOT这两个界面有什么不同的功能？"
msgstr "What are the different functions of the MCU and IOT interfaces?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:22 c9fe0954dc73490485b5b4f25365a7c9
msgid "MCU界面适用于MCU类芯片，搭配MCU SDK一起使用 IOT界面适用于带无线功能的芯片，搭配IOT SDK一起使用"
msgstr "The MCU interface is applicable to MCU-type chips and is used together with the MCU SDK. The IOT interface is applicable to chips with wireless functions and is used together with the IOT SDK."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:26 bb6a7658bf714295bfdec5fc43fc7426
msgid "烧写时，可以自动选择flash嘛？"
msgstr "Can Flash be selected automatically during programming?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:27 720234ab59b044d9842efbed2f5dd95a
msgid "烧写时，工具自动选择Flash，Flash选择优先级： 内封Flash Swap Pin > 内封FLash > 外置Flash GPIO 17-22 > 外置Flash GPIO 0-2&20-22。"
msgstr "During programming, the tool automatically selects the Flash. Flash selection priority: internal Flash Swap Pin > internal Flash > external Flash GPIO 17-22 > external Flash GPIO 0-2&20-22."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:31 6f3835d0342a4e78b886af329ae0ed73
msgid "波特率最大可以达到多少？"
msgstr "What is the maximum baud rate?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:32 81b334afa8de4b0fb43708a9ec4110bb
msgid "工具使用UART烧写时，建议的最大波特率可以达到2000000。"
msgstr "When the tool uses UART for programming, the recommended maximum baud rate can reach 2000000."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:36 3cf7d9a75732461795d8733e60f2065d
msgid "工具烧写1MB的文件，需要多久时间？"
msgstr "How long does it take for the tool to program a 1 MB file?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:37 10769a2611264cfc89b55c15f659b544
msgid "工具选择UART下载，波特率2000000时，向Winbond Flash烧写1MB文件耗时11秒左右。 该时间仅供参考，会因为Flash型号的不同有小幅变化。"
msgstr "When the tool selects UART download and the baud rate is 2000000, programming a 1 MB file to Winbond Flash takes about 11 seconds. This time is for reference only and may vary slightly depending on the Flash model."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:41 6d8c8ce9edfa448aa7ae8c072e2eab82
msgid "下载失败的原因有哪些？"
msgstr "What are the reasons for download failure?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:42 9d76d0af61ff4507992f18dc9a18a9bd
msgid "芯片没有从UART启动，导致工具和芯片握手失败"
msgstr "The chip does not boot from UART, causing the handshake between the tool and the chip to fail."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:44 fde51f8256d34642b590dd10f14f17d8
msgid "工具界面选择不合理，晶振选错等"
msgstr "The tool interface is selected incorrectly, the crystal oscillator is selected incorrectly, etc."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:46 a826e6bcc498407db29fe0716368c305
msgid "烧写文件大小超过Flash可用容量"
msgstr "The programming file size exceeds the available Flash capacity."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:48 b8b667dc0a3d4737aab8de6e58f5d599
msgid "使用外置Flash时，Flash有虚焊"
msgstr "When using external Flash, the Flash has a cold solder joint."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:50 9f2c6aacae4f4449aff6907d995cbd63
msgid "使用了工具暂不支持的Flash型号"
msgstr "A Flash model not currently supported by the tool is used."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:52 994b69b2db104d5c9bab04b9a2d54598
msgid "Flash被写保护"
msgstr "The Flash is write-protected."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:54 73337ac7ce9a46a3a8dca60801c8dd5b
msgid "工具默认使用4线模式烧写Flash，有个别型号Flash最多只支持2线模式，这种情况需要做特殊配置才能正常烧写"
msgstr "The tool uses 4-line mode to program Flash by default. A few Flash models support at most 2-line mode. In this case, special configuration is required for normal programming."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:56 f8ea73d5c18449d1be83bbfae0c5125f
msgid "工具log界面提示“Verify fail”，需要确认硬件板子设计是否能支持高波特率下载"
msgstr "The tool log interface prompts \"Verify fail\". It is necessary to confirm whether the hardware board design can support high-baud-rate downloading."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:60 c7cb3ed055ba494ea5ff0dd83a0e5f58
msgid "使用说明"
msgstr "User Guide"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:61 1d99b17ed7b44a6a9e4497bc1179da8e
msgid "具体可参考《BLDevCube用户使用手册》。路径为：docs/BLDevCube用户使用手册.pdf。"
msgstr "For details, refer to the \"BLDevCube User Manual\". Path: docs/BLDevCube用户使用手册.pdf."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:64 8c38311895b74a959de3f28cf5e2a7f9
msgid "文件烧录进去后无反应，怎么排查问题？"
msgstr "After the file is programmed, there is no response. How should the issue be troubleshot?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:65 dfbc791eebfc47389a47606c6e1861e9
msgid "在Dev Cube的IOT界面上是否勾选Partition Table(需要勾选)，是否选择了正确的分区表文件(文件名不带boot2_iap，并与实际Flash大小匹配)；"
msgstr "Check whether Partition Table is selected in the IOT interface of Dev Cube (it needs to be selected), and whether the correct partition table file is selected (the file name should not contain boot2_iap and should match the actual Flash size);"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:67 17cfe17010db46ffafcf0e663ad5db11
msgid "在Dev Cube的IOT界面上是否勾选Boot2 Bin(bl602需要勾选，bl702不需要勾选)；"
msgstr "Check whether Boot2 Bin is selected in the IOT interface of Dev Cube (bl602 needs to be selected, bl702 does not need to be selected);"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:69 eb30335611604329852879f16325d1c0
msgid "接上串口板，烧写其它能正常工作的bin文件(带有UART打印)，排除硬件问题；"
msgstr "Connect a serial port board and program another bin file that works normally (with UART printing) to rule out hardware issues;"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:71 31e81fa6983b4f60ac4b418f9f279481
msgid "是否修改了主函数名(bl602主函数为bfl_main，bl702主函数为bl702_main)；"
msgstr "Check whether the main function name has been modified (the main function for bl602 is bfl_main, and the main function for bl702 is bl702_main);"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:73 87df8d07172e432c97b85452a287fdd0
msgid "用FreedomStudio调试，是否能运行到主函数，不能的话，检查是否修改了portASM.S或flash.ld；"
msgstr "Use FreedomStudio for debugging. Check whether execution can reach the main function. If not, check whether portASM.S or Flash.ld has been modified;"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:75 7004b289f7494904b684cd131443a940
msgid "是否修改了UART初始化代码，是否将UART_TX引脚配置成了其它功能或配置成了高阻，UART时钟是否被禁掉；"
msgstr "Check whether the UART initialization code has been modified, whether the UART_TX pin has been configured as another function or configured as high impedance, and whether the UART clock has been disabled;"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:77 d0f4cf0a6e5a4be2ba11e305eef49cd3
msgid "是否修改了printf函数或使用了其它打印函数；"
msgstr "Check whether the printf function has been modified or another print function is used;"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:79 dcd230d715da4842bd9a3be88cae0a6a
msgid "是否修改了系统时钟；"
msgstr "Check whether the system clock has been modified."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:83 4e55a9c1f66a4f0993cf353b59276a71
msgid "Ai-WB2系列模组烧写是否需要接IO8引脚"
msgstr "Does the Ai-WB2 series module need to connect the IO8 pin for programming?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:84 053990b1e17f481c9b32acf687d45d28
msgid "不需要，只需要接四根线，点击烧录软件的下载按钮后给模块硬件复位即可下载"
msgstr "No. Only four wires need to be connected. After clicking the download button in the programming software, reset the module hardware to start downloading."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:89 deeecd914dd849cf8d46bb464ffeb11b
msgid "工厂批量烧写工具"
msgstr "Factory Batch Programming Tool"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:92 67155a16b69c46e28844f3cb22080948
msgid "批量烧写工具支持哪些烧写模式?"
msgstr "Which programming modes are supported by the batch programming tool?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:93 d5cc651c459442ff9da3ce4dcdc12d8d
msgid "单文件模式： 工具界面指定烧写文件和指定烧写地址，工具会将指定文件烧写到Flash指定地址上"
msgstr "Single-file mode: Specify the programming file and programming address in the tool interface, and the tool will program the specified file to the specified address in Flash."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:95 389ab253af5044f2976545c673639804
msgid "开发模式： 可以在配置文件中指定多个烧写文件和对应的烧写地址，工具会一次性烧写多个文件到Flash对应的烧写地址上"
msgstr "Development mode: Multiple programming files and corresponding programming addresses can be specified in the configuration file, and the tool will program multiple files to the corresponding Flash addresses at one time."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:97 dc6620a7451541929d1690d1cd7a23a4
msgid "动态模式： 支持动态生成烧写文件，适用于一机一码等烧写文件需要动态改变的场景，动态文件生成功能需要按具体需求定制"
msgstr "Dynamic mode: Supports dynamic generation of programming files. It is suitable for scenarios where the programming file needs to change dynamically, such as one device with one unique code. The dynamic file generation function needs to be customized according to specific requirements."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:101 e697e5e0a34a4b2089b62079df237fdb
msgid "批量烧写工具对于芯片上电时序有什么样的要求？"
msgstr "What are the power-on timing requirements of the batch programming tool for the chip?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:102 28974fd6e7bf4a3ab9e7d9af0b4b17be
msgid "批量烧写工具在做烧写任务前，需要让芯片从UART启动。 建议使用博流烧写板控制芯片的上电时序，确保批量生产时，烧写的稳定性。 博流烧写板和烧写工具之前会有一套软硬件之间协同控制芯片上电时序的流程。"
msgstr "Before performing a programming task, the batch programming tool needs to make the chip boot from UART. It is recommended to use the Bouffalo Lab programming board to control the chip power-on timing to ensure programming stability during mass production. There is a set of software-hardware cooperative processes between the Bouffalo Lab programming board and the programming tool for controlling the chip power-on timing."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:107 82b388fc87374c31be7fddd72df2587a
msgid "使用说明？"
msgstr "User Guide?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:108 73a70a4c46cd4134a3de14d6ce68a650
msgid "具体可参考《BL批量烧写工具使用手册》。"
msgstr "For details, refer to the \"BL Batch Programming Tool User Manual\"."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:111 b48e6d876ada4b029b018be3812bda2b
msgid "请问WB2模组是否买了TTL模块就可以实现供电以及烧录功能？"
msgstr "Can the WB2 module be powered and programmed after buying a TTL module?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/tools.rst:112 45d71d52e2eb4472b1ff06973aa533b6
msgid "是的，TTL `购买链接  <https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.3-c-s.w4002-24271435830.9.45c84853LqwXqs&id=565546260974>`__"
msgstr "Yes. TTL `Purchase link  <https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.3-c-s.w4002-24271435830.9.45c84853LqwXqs&id=565546260974>`__"
